{"tid":1768703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北約聯合聲明將首點明中國崛起帶來西方文明挑戰","createTime":"2019-12-04T09:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T10:28:00.000Z","uid":125193,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de509f2e45c27e0540159f72f430aa30dbfe2b6a","tid":1768703,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"北約在倫敦舉行峰會，據報會在聯合聲明中，首次承認中國崛起帶來機遇與挑戰，並會批准一份內部報告，擬定應對中國的行動計劃。<br />\n<br />\n北約秘書長斯托爾滕貝格說，中國崛起對所有北約盟國帶來安全影響，中國的影響力正觸及北約邊界，同時大力投資網絡與歐洲基建，北約不是要製造新對手，而是要以平衡方式回應中國的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，聯合聲明亦會強調有必要建立「安全而有彈性」的通信系統，尤其是在5G技術建設上，表明北約與西方各國，普遍對華為等中國企業在下一代通信網絡的地位，感到越來越焦慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495951-20191204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495951-20191204.htm&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=9780ec2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495951-20191204.htm&h=460af8a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495951-20191204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\noh no <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c53d8f424e8740ddbb22140c59da53f0fa52e25","tid":1768703,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"根本就係文明世界對不文明世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327fe97a45dcda90a6517fa6ec0e22471fc41059","tid":1768703,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"似係真係圍攻中國"},{"pid":"fb52dd1cc9eef02ce480ed01f8a9a5aa64ba91da","tid":1768703,"uid":125193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"人